WEBVTT

42:26.470 --> 42:29.030 line:80%
He said he would leave with me for now.

42:29.830 --> 42:30.870 line:80%
But what about the future?

42:30.870 --> 42:32.400 line:80%
Why worry about the future?

42:33.310 --> 42:34.160 line:80%
Since he married into your family,

42:34.160 --> 42:35.920 line:80%
you have to take the initiative.
